snippet.title: Lost Soul Aside ChinaJoy2018 Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer of Lost Soul Aside shown on ChinaJoy2018 Sony Playstation conference.
Game under development does not represent final quality.
Check more information at: https://www.facebook.com/lostsoulaside/
Music by Tybercore.
VO by Joe Millonzi(Kazer&Arena) and 
Sara Secora(Zenthya).
